        "excerpt":  "You\u0027ve finally found the person you want to spend the rest of your life with. Congratulations! The next step is to start planning the wedding of your dreams. And one of the most important decisions you\u0027ll make is choosin...",
        "metaDescription":  "Make your wedding day unforgettable with our perfect banquet hall in Mississauga. Elegant venue, exceptional service.",
        "category":  null,
